=== Age-based Content Gating ===
Age-based Content Gating would automatically enable Content Gating for users under 18 for every filter except Extreme Horror. This was revealed in the 22 November 2023 Developer Update<ref>[https://ask.vrchat.com/t/developer-update-22-november-2023/20878#h-202342-open-beta-6 Developer Update - 22 November, 2023]</ref>. Due to issues with the system in regards to users having the incorrect Date of Birth on their VRChat account and the way creators label their content, it has been disabled as of December 7th, 2023<ref name="7Dec2023DevUpdate"/>. It has been suggested this will be reimplemented with [[Age Verification]] in the future, however there is no confirmation as to when or how it will be done.

